text: Studying in Stansfield got me a second class honours in banking and finance, because the first year I studied at SIM and the lecturers weren't so helpful so I ended up failing that year. And then I swtiched to Stansfield. I re-did my first year and I did soooo much better and the second and third year were good too. Here they helped me focus a lot and they are so people oriented
biggest mistake ever. tiny profit seeking school. teachers offer zero help beside talking down and calling names. just dont.
Ex law student from this college, 100% not recommended.
